COMMAND init
SYNOPSIS: python3 scripts/cypilot.py init [options]
DESCRIPTION: Initialize Cypilot config and minimal adapter for a project
WORKFLOW: adapter

ARGUMENTS:

OPTIONS:
  --project-root  <path>  Project root directory to create .cypilot-config.json in (default: parent of Cypilot core)
  --cypilot-root  <path>  Explicit Cypilot core root (optional override)
  --adapter-path  <path>  Adapter directory path relative to project root (default: .cypilot-adapter)
  --project-name  <string>  Project name used in adapter AGENTS.md (default: project root folder name)
  --yes  <boolean>  Do not prompt; accept defaults
  --dry-run  <boolean>  Compute changes without writing files
  --force  <boolean>  Overwrite existing files

EXIT CODES:
  0  Initialization successful
  1  Error (conflicts, invalid paths, etc.)

EXAMPLE:
  $ python3 scripts/cypilot.py init
  $ python3 scripts/cypilot.py init --yes
  $ python3 scripts/cypilot.py init --project-root . --adapter-path .cypilot-adapter --yes
  $ python3 scripts/cypilot.py init --dry-run
  $ python3 scripts/cypilot.py init --force

RELATED:
  - @CLI.adapter-info
  - @CLI.agents
  - @Workflow.adapter
